author: Midwinter Minis
description:
No not GW lol. As if they would send me anything without signing a 12 page legal agreement.

Huge thanks to Wargames Exclusive for sending me out this bundle of goodies. Disclaimer: they didn't pay me to make this video, but they did gift me everything shown in the video.

This video is a follow-up to this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j4qeEAG-Cb4

The items they sent me:

ORK GROT GUZZLA: https://wargameexclusive.com/shop/orks/ork-grot-guzzla/
